<section class="section-padding bg-navy">
  <div class="container-main px-4">
    <h2 class="animate-on-scroll font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-12">
      What Property Owners Say
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="animate-on-scroll bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold fill-gold" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
          "Saadi came in on budget and ahead of schedule on a 120-unit
          renovation program. The quality of finish work was a cut above
          what we had seen from other contractors at this price point."
        </p>
        <div>
          <p class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Marcus T.</p>
          <p class="text-gold text-xs mt-1">Owner, Parkside Villas — Houston, TX</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold fill-gold" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
          "We needed an occupied renovation program that kept residents
          in place. Saadi phased the work intelligently, communicated
          clearly with our property management team, and delivered
          every unit on the agreed timeline."
        </p>
        <div>
          <p class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Diana R.</p>
          <p class="text-gold text-xs mt-1">Asset Manager, Creekwood Apartments — Houston Metro</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10">
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold fill-gold" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
          "The scope documentation and per-unit cost breakdown Saadi
          provided was more detailed than anything we had received
          from larger firms. It gave us full confidence going into
          the capital program."
        </p>
        <div>
          <p class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">James O.</p>
          <p class="text-gold text-xs mt-1">Regional Manager, Cypress Ridge Communities — Katy, TX</p>
        </div>
      </div>
